---
title: Mexican-Style Black Bean Soup with Charred Corn & Chilli Tortilla Chips
description: One good way to beat the chill? Channel the flavours of Mexico into a hearty soup with black beans and rainbow veggies. A pinch of chilli flakes, some warm tortilla chips and Mexican-style spices bring a warmth that'll make you feel toasty inside.

